327
00:13:10.391 --> 00:13:12.627
And you. your sleight of hand
was advanced. Good dexterity.

328
00:13:12.694 --> 00:13:14.696
You're quick
and nimble on your feet.
Really. I was impressed.

329
00:13:14.763 --> 00:13:16.463
